This widget can be used to set a dynamic model's phenotype (PC or NPC) to any desired.

Use the Commands:
SetVarInt base_phenotype ## to set what the PC will turn back into. This will usually be 0 (for normal).

SetVarInt alt_phenotype ## to set what the PC will turn into. Example: SetVarInt alt_phenotype 19 will set the arcane "hovering" phenotype.

SetVarString phenotype_name to give a custom name to the phenotype. Example: Drow-Levitation

## Represents the numerical value of the phenotype. This is found in phenotype.2da or on the forums.
